  "title": "WAREHOUSE ASSISTANT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will handle the picking, packing, sorting, and checking of goods to ensure accuracy and quality. You will load and unload cartons safely and assist with daily warehouse operations while maintaining a clean and safe work environment.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Pick and pack goods accurately to fulfill orders and maintain inventory integrity</li><li>Sort and check items to identify damaged or missing goods before shipment</li><li>Load and unload cartons safely to support efficient warehouse flow</li><li>Perform housekeeping tasks to keep the warehouse clean and organized for operational efficiency</li><li>Inspect items for damage or missing parts to ensure quality control before dispatch</li><li>Assist with daily warehouse operations to support smooth logistics processes</li><li>Follow safety rules and procedures consistently to maintain a safe working environment</li></ul>",
