    "description": "<p>JJ Express Services was established in 1998, JJ Express specializes in document and parcel delivery island wide throughout Singapore. We have a team of dedicated and professional staff who are committed in providing quality services with sincerity and dedication.</p>\n<p>Our company's motto is to continiously enhance our services so as to ensure total customer satisfaction, respond immediately to changing customer neds, pursue relentlessly to achieve service excellence abd to offer competitive rates for your customers.</p>\n<p>Our professional team will alwasy ensure your packages arrive at the intended destination without a htich and even take a step further to notifying you as soon as the packages arrive at its destination.</p>\n<p>With a reputation for excellence, all our customers hiring our service is to ensure their satisfaction to meet business needs in the most timely and relible way. With JJ Express, you have more flexibility when seeking solutions to your most urgent needs in today's fast-paced establishment. Whenever your critical delivery needs arise, just call us and leave the rest in our good hands.</p>\n<p>In addition, we are also a Gebiz-registered company with an S4 clearance level.</p>\n<p>Our bankers are DBS main branch, we are completely covered by AXA and NTUC insurance for all road movement islandwide.</p>",
